review_summary: These scissors are so useful, cost-effective
review_text: These scissors are so useful, cost-effective, and handy that we keep a pair in nearly every room of the house. And in the kitchen, we keep TWO pairs -- one to cut up herbs and such with (those stay in the knife drawer), and one to open bags and cut off tags with (that pair stays in the junk drawer). I've even put the kitchen pair in the dishwasher several times (which I'm sure can't be recommended, but I do it anyway), and they're still sharp. The handles are comfortable, and the price is right -- I highly recommend buying multiple packages, as you'll find great uses for them everywhere!

Anyone who draws needs this pen.  It is also great for calligraphy.
